## 2. Charcoal Noir Historical (1900s-1940s)
![Charcoal Noir Historical - Ottoman Battle](C:\Users\Admin\.gemini\antigravity\brain\1e4b8255-ac37-4f5b-a349-2576ada2ea6c\ottoman_charcoal_noir_1775187879390.png)

